_sText:
I put together a recreation of the map of the fourth level mission of SWAT 3 (the big house), complete with textures (credit to the creator of Poolday as some of his textures were used for the pool and bathrooms), textures come pakratted meaning that you will automatically get the textures along with anyone else who you play with.

This is my first map upload to this site, if you find any major faults/glitches comment and I will fix it.  

Check out the screenshots =)

Enjoy! =D
